cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

The paper deals with the development and training of deep neural networks for vision tasks, specifically focusing on the problem of noise attacks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Among these, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the topic of the paper.
